**Car loan EMIs** in India typically range from ₹1,500 to ₹3,000 per lakh borrowed at current market rates of 9–13% p.a. for 1–7 year tenures. New car loans are cheaper than used car loans. Most banks offer up to 90% of the on-road price for new cars and 80% for used vehicles. Use this calculator to find your exact monthly outflow.
